          UNINORTE - MINTIC © | Email: info@phillips.com | Teléfono: (+57) 601
          235 846.</p></div>
    </footer>
    <!-- Bootstrap core JS-->
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    ></script>
    <!-- Core theme JS-->
    <script src="/static/js/scripts.js"></script>
    <!-- Scrips del Registro de usuarios -->
    <script src="/static/js/registroUsuario.js"></script>
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/2c36e9b7b1.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>